  <bioghist id="aspace_47d42541facac8ef268cfccce7c6013b">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>Records from 1967 to 1984 are from the Office of Vice Provost; records from 1985 to 1986 are from the office of the Vice President for Academic Programs. The name change did not reflect any change in personnel or responsibilities.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_871df5c41b450e2cffdf45ac665866a6">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Files of Larry I. Palmer, including general correspondence and miscellaneous reports. Includes records of the Subcommittee for Minority Education, 1984 and records of the Cornell Commission on Undergraduate Education. Also, records of the Cornell University Libraries Director Search and miscellaneous reports.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <arrangement id="aspace_e6e89ab416aeb576d8764eef92ced4bc">
